quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,"Reenee juulЙ—e Й—en, e juulde hakkundeere nden. DaranoЙ—on Alla ko o toЖҙЖҙiniiЙ“e"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppayЙ“e maa waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e. Si on hoolike, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla nden wano no anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: ko wasiyanagol suddiiЙ“e Й“en dakmitorЙ—um haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiЕӢgol Й“e. Si Й“e yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere. Alla ko fooluЙ—o ГұeeГұuЙ—o."
  2,241,"No woodani Й“en seeraaЙ“e: dakamitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri. ko goonga fawiiЙ—o goongЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje makko Й—en, mbela joo on haqqilay."
  2,243,"E a tinaali Й“en njaltunooЙ“e e galleeji mu'un, kamЙ“e ko Й“e guluuje (ujunaaji ), ngam reenagol maayde, Allaahu on daalani Й“e: "Maayee", refti o wuurniti Й“e? Pellet Alla ko Jom Й“ural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en njaanataa (njettataa) [Alla]."
  2,244,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko nanoowo annduЙ—o"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on Гұawloowo Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere, o sowitana mo nde cowalle Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e? Alla no Й“iЙ—ttina himo YaГұГұa, ko fa'de ka nakko ruttoto-Й—on."